#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.85"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.85:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.85:0.2"
msgid "9. Samaṇavagga "
msgstr "9. Ascetics "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.85:0.3"
msgid "85. Sekkhasutta "
msgstr "85. A Trainee "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.85:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an3.85:2.1"
msgid "“‘Sekho, sekho’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this person called ‘a trainee’. "

msgctxt "an3.85:2.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, sekho hotī”ti? "
msgstr "How is a trainee defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.85:2.3"
msgid "“Sikkhatīti kho, bhikkhu, tasmā sekhoti vuccati. "
msgstr "“They train, mendicant, that’s why they’re called ‘a trainee’. "

msgctxt "an3.85:2.4"
msgid "Kiñca sikkhati? "
msgstr "What is their training? "

msgctxt "an3.85:2.5"
msgid "Adhisīlampi sikkhati, adhicittampi sikkhati, adhipaññampi sikkhati. "
msgstr "They train in the higher ethics, the higher mind, and the higher wisdom. "

msgctxt "an3.85:2.6"
msgid "Sikkhatīti kho, bhikkhu, tasmā sekhoti vuccatīti. "
msgstr "They train, that’s why they’re called ‘a trainee’. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an3.85:3.1"
msgid "Sekhassa sikkhamānassa, "
msgstr "As a trainee trains, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.85:3.2"
msgid "ujumaggānusārino; "
msgstr "following the straight road, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.85:3.3"
msgid "Khayasmiṃ paṭhamaṃ ñāṇaṃ, "
msgstr "first they know about ending; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.85:3.4"
msgid "tato aññā anantarā. "
msgstr "enlightenment follows in the same lifetime. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
#. VAR: aññāvimuttassa → aññāvimuttiyā (mr)
msgctxt "an3.85:4.1"
msgid "Tato aññāvimuttassa, "
msgstr "After that, to that poised one, freed by enlightenment, "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: ñāṇaṃ ve → ñāṇañca (mr)
msgctxt "an3.85:4.2"
msgid "ñāṇaṃ ve hoti tādino; "
msgstr "with the ending of the fetters of rebirth, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.85:4.3"
msgid "Akuppā me vimuttīti, "
msgstr "the knowledge comes: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.85:4.4"
msgid "bhavasaṃyojanakkhaye”ti. "
msgstr "‘My freedom is unshakable.’” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.85:4.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
